Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.885
Availability, reliability, resilience.
可用性 可靠性 弹性 

00:00:03.885 --> 00:00:07.560
Availability is how often a system operates as expected.
可用性是系统按预期运行的频率 

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:12.030
This is typically measured as a percentage of the time a system is running.
这通常以系统运行时的百分比来度量 

00:00:12.030 --> 00:00:15.270
Reliability is how likely something is to be
可靠性是

00:00:15.270 --> 00:00:18.990
operating as expected at any given point in time.
在任何给定时间点按预期运行 

00:00:18.990 --> 00:00:26.440
Resiliency is how quickly and easily a system can be brought back online after an outage.
弹性是在中断后 系统可以快速和轻松地重新联机的方式 
